headings.text: Have you ever felt out of place in your own body?
Have you ever walked with a sense that everyone else seems to know more about your body than YOU do?
This disconnect is not how we are made to live.
From the skin to the spinal cord, to each beautiful swath of fascia and tissue, our bodies are designed to communicate with our conscious mind in a language beyond words.
We are made to KNOW ourselves.
At Umi our mission is to honor the unique mind, body, and spirit of each individual member, from the womb to the beginning of forever.
With us, start feeling like you’re right where you need to be.

headings.text: Our journey can be long, troubled and challenging.
This lecture series is curated to give that journey a little more hope.

Lectures that are open to the public will be labeled as their dates and times are announced.  Email Office@umicharlotte.com to sign up or get on our event news list for regular announcements. Makes sure you add this email to your contact list so you don’t miss any news updates!
